Modul htl.steyr.javafx_minesweeper_tplatzer

module htl.steyr.javafx_minesweeper_tplatzer
Defines the htl.steyr.javafx_minesweeper_tplatzer module.

This module contains the Minesweeper application, implemented using JavaFX. It specifies dependencies required for UI rendering, external controls, HTTP communication, and desktop functionalities.

Required Modules:

  • javafx.controls - Provides JavaFX UI components.
  • org.controlsfx.controls - Includes additional JavaFX UI controls.
  • java.desktop - Enables AWT and Swing functionalities for audio and file handling.
  • java.net.http - Allows communication with external web services.

Exported Packages:

  • htl.steyr.javafx_minesweeper_tplatzer.app - Contains the main application entry points.
  • htl.steyr.javafx_minesweeper_tplatzer.controller - Handles user interactions and UI control.
  • htl.steyr.javafx_minesweeper_tplatzer.model - Manages data structures and persistence.
  • htl.steyr.javafx_minesweeper_tplatzer.service - Provides auxiliary services like audio and networking.
